    <h1>Territory and member safety.</h1>
    <p class="lead">The treaty is a relationship to the land. Part of that is knowing who is organizing in the territory in ways that touch the people who live here. This page gathers what credible, public bodies have documented about such groups, with a source for every claim. It relays reporting; it does not make accusations, and it names no private community members. Where the record is thin, it says so.</p>
